originalText.text: I had the worst experience ever with this club. I’m going to start off by saying the security staff from this place is hostile and rude. Horrible treatment and approach, particularly from the female security. The rest of the staff that are in the front before entering the club don’t even try to solve a problem that you bring to their attention. The ambience is good but I was so thrown off, disappointed and utterly disgusted by the approach I received from the female security. The coat check area also gives you a hard time if you happen to lose your ticket. Overall it was a disappointing experience because I had a good time inside the club; however the inconveniences I kept having since I got in until I got out were unpleasant. This place gives you issues for the smallest thing. I wouldn’t recommend.

originalText.text: I honestly have never had a worst  experience at a club. Bunch of customers left violated and scammed. Spare your time, wallet, and dignity from this place. Don’t give your money to people who have no problem spitting in your face: Went there last night with family and friends, after we each payed $50, about 8 of us, to reserve a spot, only for us to get there and be told that the club was max capacity, only we weren’t the only group who didn’t get in, outside were also other groups, who also reserved tables, who were not being allowed inside. They were max capacity, but multiple reservations were outside waiting to get in, who took all our tables? And they didn’t mind letting some people in every once in a while, if they payed $80. Some other people were also offered to go in, only if they payed $200. As if they enjoy spitting in their customers’ faces, they then offered some of the groups outside, with reservations, a spot in the club, but away from the main area: Only if we each payed an extra $80 on top of the 100s of dollars we had already payed.

originalText.text: Spent over an hour and a half on line and did not get it in after making a reservation for 10 people. Rude security and promoters that were angry at the crowd for their own disorganization. I used to come to this place in 2019 and it was such a different vibe such a disappointment. Don’t bother or waste your time.
